## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="8daf5-102"><xref:System.ServiceModel.Activities.CorrelationScope> アクティビティは、子アクティビティのみに表示される暗黙的な <xref:System.ServiceModel.Activities.CorrelationHandle> を管理します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8daf5-102">The <xref:System.ServiceModel.Activities.CorrelationScope> activity maintains an implicit <xref:System.ServiceModel.Activities.CorrelationHandle> that is only visible to child activities.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8daf5-103"><xref:System.ServiceModel.Activities.CorrelationScope.CorrelatesWith%2A> プロパティは、ユーザーによって設定された場合、暗黙的な <xref:System.ServiceModel.Activities.CorrelationScope> ハンドルとして使用されます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8daf5-103">When the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Activities.CorrelationScope.CorrelatesWith%2A> property is set by the user, it will be used as the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Activities.CorrelationScope> implicit handle.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8daf5-104"><xref:System.ServiceModel.Activities.CorrelationScope> が入れ子になっていると、内側のスコープの子は外側のスコープの暗黙的なハンドルにアクセスできません。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8daf5-104">In the case of nested <xref:System.ServiceModel.Activities.CorrelationScope>, children of the inner scope cannot access implicit handle of the outer scope.</span></span>  
  
   
  
